csvw:title: AgentAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to another Agent.

csvw:title: AgentIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for an Agent.

csvw:title: AgentMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing an Agent as content in a Media entity.

csvw:title: Agent
skos:definition: A person, group, organization or other entity that can act.

csvw:title: ChronometricAgeAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a chrono:ChronometricAge.

csvw:title: ChronometricAgeAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a chrono:ChronometricAge.

csvw:title: ChronometricAgeMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a chrono:ChronometricAge as content of a Media entity.

csvw:title: ChronometricAgeProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in the determination of a chrono:ChronometricAge.

csvw:title: ChronometricAgeReference
skos:definition: A bibliographic reference in which a chrono:ChronometricAge is mentioned.

csvw:title: ChronometricAge
skos:definition: An approximation of temporal position (in the sense conveyed by https://www.w3.org/TR/owl-time/#time:TemporalPosition) that is supported by evidence.

csvw:title: CollectionAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a Collection.

csvw:title: CollectionAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a Collection.

csvw:title: CollectionMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a Collection as content of a Media entity.

csvw:title: Collection
skos:definition: A persistent formal repository in which dwc:MaterialEntities and/or Media are preserved.

csvw:title: EventAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a dwc:Event.

csvw:title: EventAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a dwc:Event.

csvw:title: EventIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a dwc:Event.

csvw:title: EventMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a dwc:Event as content of a Media entity.

csvw:title: EventProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in a dwc:Event.

csvw:title: EventReference
skos:definition: A bibliographic reference in which a dwc:Event is mentioned.

csvw:title: Event
skos:definition: An action, process, or set of circumstances occurring at a dcterms:Location during a period of time.

csvw:title: GeologicalContextMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a dwc:GeologicalContext as content of a Media entity.

csvw:title: GeologicalContext
skos:definition: A set of geological designations, such as stratigraphy, that qualifies a dwc:Event.

csvw:title: IdentificationAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a dwc:Identification.

csvw:title: IdentificationTaxon
skos:definition: A construct of components and positions of dwc:scientificNames in a dwc:Identification.

csvw:title: Identification
skos:definition: A taxonomic determination (i.e., the assignment of dwc:Taxa to dwc:Organisms).

csvw:title: MaterialAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a dwc:MaterialEntity.

csvw:title: MaterialAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a dwc:MaterialEntity.

csvw:title: MaterialIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a dwc:MaterialEntity.

csvw:title: MaterialMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a dwc:MaterialEntity as content of a Media entity.

csvw:title: MaterialProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in the treatment of a dwc:MaterialEntity.

csvw:title: MaterialReference
skos:definition: A bibliographic reference in which a dwc:MaterialEntity is mentioned.

csvw:title: Material
skos:definition: An entity that can be identified, exist for some period of time, and consist in whole or in part of physical matter while it exists.

csvw:title: MediaAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a Media entity.

csvw:title: MediaAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a Media entity.

csvw:title: MediaIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a Media entity.

csvw:title: Media
skos:definition: A dcmi:MediaType (dcmi:Sounds, dcmi:StillImages, dcmi:MovingImages or dcmi:Text) with other entities as content.

csvw:title: MolecularProtocolAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a MolecularProtocol.

csvw:title: MolecularProtocolAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a MolecularProtocol.

csvw:title: MolecularProtocolReference
skos:definition: A bibliographic reference in which a MolecularProtocol is mentioned.

csvw:title: MolecularProtocol
skos:definition: A protocol used to derive and identify a nucleotide sequence from a dwc:MaterialEntity.

csvw:title: NucleotideAnalysisAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a NucleotideAnalysis.

csvw:title: NucleotideAnalysis
skos:definition: A link between a NucleotideSequence and a dwc:Event and a dwc:MaterialEntity from which it was derived, using a specified Protocol.

csvw:title: NucleotideSequence
skos:definition: A digital representation of a nucleotide sequence.

csvw:title: OccurrenceAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a dwc:Occurrence.

csvw:title: OccurrenceAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a dwc:Occurrence.

csvw:title: OccurrenceIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a dwc:Occurrence.

csvw:title: OccurrenceMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a dwc:Occurrence as content of a Media entity.

csvw:title: OccurrenceProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in the determination of a dwc:Occurrence.

csvw:title: OccurrenceReference
skos:definition: A bibliographic reference in which a dwc:Occurrence is mentioned.

csvw:title: Occurrence
skos:definition: A state of a dwc:Organism in a dwc:Event.

csvw:title: OrganismInteractionAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to an OrganismInteraction.

csvw:title: OrganismInteractionAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about an OrganismInteraction.

csvw:title: OrganismInteractionMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing an OrganismInteraction as content of a Media entity.

csvw:title: OrganismInteractionReference
skos:definition: A bibliographic reference in which an OrganismInteraction is mentioned.

csvw:title: OrganismInteraction
skos:definition: An interaction between two dwc:Organisms during a dwc:Event.

csvw:title: PhylogeneticTreeAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a PhylogeneticTree.

csvw:title: PhylogeneticTreeIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a PhylogeneticTree.

csvw:title: PhylogeneticTreeMedia
skos:definition: A link establishing a PhylogeneticTree as content of a Media entity.

csvw:title: PhylogeneticTreeProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in the determination of a PhylogeneticTree.

csvw:title: PhylogeneticTreeReference
skos:definition: A bibliographic reference in which a PhylogeneticTree is mentioned.

csvw:title: PhylogeneticTreeTipAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a PhylogeneticTreeTip.

csvw:title: PhylogeneticTreeTip
skos:definition: A group of Taxa at the end of a branch of a PhylogeneticTree as determined from relationships between dwc:Organisms.

csvw:title: PhylogeneticTree
skos:definition: A branching diagram that shows the evolutionary relationships between dwc:Organisms.

csvw:title: ProtocolReference
skos:definition: A bibliographic reference in which a Protocol is mentioned.

csvw:title: Protocol
skos:definition: A method used during an action.

csvw:title: Reference
skos:definition: A bibliographic reference in which an entity is mentioned.

csvw:title: Relationship
skos:definition: A specification for a relationship of a subject entity to a related entity.

csvw:title: SurveyAgentRole
skos:definition: A role filled by an Agent with respect to a Survey.

csvw:title: SurveyAssertion
skos:definition: An Assertion made by an Agent about a Survey.

csvw:title: SurveyIdentifier
skos:definition: An identifier for a Survey.

csvw:title: SurveyProtocol
skos:definition: A link establishing a Protocol used in a Survey.

csvw:title: SurveyReference
skos:definition: A bibliographic reference in which a Survey is mentioned.

csvw:title: SurveyTarget
skos:definition: A specification of a characteristic of dwc:Occurrence that was included or excluded in a Survey.

csvw:title: Survey
skos:definition: A biotic survey.
